(137, 1, '2014-01-10 19:20:16', '2014-01-10 19:20:16', 'LOS ANGELES - March 18, 2013 - Oakwood Worldwide, the global leader in corporate housing and serviced apartments, recently announced Insurance Housing Solutions, offering full-service and cost-effective emergency housing solutions to policyholders, adjusters, first responders, restoration providers and catastrophe response teams. With full-scale insurance housing capabilities, expertise in temporary housing solutions and the largest footprint of inventory in the U.S. and Canada, Insurance Housing Solutions offers the value of a one-stop shop to the insurance industry.\r\n\r\n"We''re pleased to be offering the industry''s most robust and complete solution," said Joan McCarthy Mack vice president of Oakwood Worldwide''s Insurance Housing Solutions. "With our recent acquisition of the ExecuStay® brand, the strength of the Oakwood® brand and our preferred partnership with Marriott® International, we now provide access to the broadest selection of housing, including Marriott-branded hotels, apartments, condos and single-family homes, along with a deeply experienced and dedicated team and 24/7/365 customer care."\r\n\r\nIn addition, Insurance Housing Solutions offers:\r\n\r\na dedicated team of Additional Living Expenses (ALE) specialists who understand policy limits and budgets\r\nflexible leasing terms and billing options, including customized invoices and reports to help adjusters track multiple accounts\r\na single point of contact for seamless placement, and\r\nMarriott Rewards® points for policyholders staying at any ExecuStay location in the U.S., for more than 30 days.\r\nTo learn more about Insurance Housing Solutions, visit <a href="http://insurancehousingsolutions.com">www.insurancehousingsolutions.com.</a> For 24-hour claims service, call 1-800-990-9292.', 'Oakwood Worldwide&reg; Launches Insurance Housing Solutions<sup>TM</sup>', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oakwood-worldwide-launches-insurance-housing-solutionstm', '', '', '2014-01-21 00:48:26', '2014-01-21 00:48:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/2014/?post_type=press_releases&#038;p=137', 0, 'press_releases', '', 0),
