(152, 1, '2014-01-17 22:10:09', '2014-01-17 22:10:09', 'Jill Chapman is senior vice president of global sales and marketing for Oakwood Worldwide. She leads sales and marketing strategy, while managing global operations outside the United States. Her responsibilities include strengthening the Oakwood Worldwide family of brands, and delivering targeted, client-driven solutions.\r\n\r\nChapman brings more than 25 years of dynamic sales leadership and customer service experience to this position. Previously, she served as vice president of sales for Oakwood Worldwide''s western region, during which time she helped bring innovative customer and sales solutions to many Fortune 1000 companies.\r\n\r\nBefore joining Oakwood Worldwide, Jill held business development and sales management positions at RR Donnelley with progressive responsibility over an 18-year period. As regional sales manager there, she consistently grew revenue and was accomplished around talent development. Three of her associates received the company''s Rookie of the Year award with three other associates winning Sales Associate of the Year awards.\r\n\r\nChapman earned her bachelor''s degree in American Studies from Florida State University. A resident of Southern California, Chapman is involved with volunteer work at her children''s schools as well as fundraising for community service organizations that benefit women''s shelters and families with medical emergencies.\r\n\r\nHer favorite place to travel? Sri Lanka, because of the beautiful country and the people who are so charming and friendly.', 'Jill Chapman', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'jill-chapman', '', '', '2014-01-17 22:10:09', '2014-01-17 22:10:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/2014/?post_type=executive-committee&#038;p=152', 0, 'executive-committee', '', 0),
