(201, 1, '2014-01-21 20:34:45', '2014-01-21 20:34:45', 'Oakwood Worldwide has received top category honors in the 2013 Nationwide Relocating Employee Survey© conducted by Trippel Survey & Research LLC.  Out of all temporary housing providers surveyed, Oakwood Worldwide received the highest performance score based on "overall level of service satisfaction." This is the company''s second consecutive year receiving recognition as a top performer in this survey.', 'Nationwide Relocating Employee Survey', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nationwide-relocating-employee-survey', '', '', '2014-01-21 20:35:55', '2014-01-21 20:35:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/2014/?post_type=awards&#038;p=201', 0, 'awards', '', 0),
(202, 1, '2014-01-21 20:35:46', '2014-01-21 20:35:46', 'Oakwood Worldwide has received top category honors in the 2013 Nationwide Relocating Employee Survey© conducted by Trippel Survey & Research LLC.  Out of all temporary housing providers surveyed, Oakwood Worldwide received the highest performance score based on "overall level of service satisfaction." This is the company''s second consecutive year receiving recognition as a top performer in this survey.', 'Nationwide Relocating Employee Survey', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '201-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-01-21 20:35:46', '2014-01-21 20:35:46', '', 201, 'http://localhost:8888/2014/2014/01/201-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(203, 1, '2014-01-21 20:40:49', '2014-01-21 20:40:49', 'Oakwood Worldwide received both the Commitment to Excellence Gold and Silver Supplier Innovation Awards for the second year in a row. Presented at the Cartus Global Network Conference, the Commitment to Excellence Gold Award recognizes extraordinary service. Oakwood Worldwide was also recognized for innovation for Echosign by Adobe®, a system which centralizes and automates all guest paperwork, including leases, with easy access via smartphones and tablets. This technology reduces the average time to complete and return a lease from three days to 24 hours.', 'Commitment to Excellence Gold and Silver Supplier Innovation Awards', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'commitment-to-excellence-gold-and-silver-supplier-innovation-awards', '', '', '2014-01-21 20:54:07', '2014-01-21 20:54:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/2014/?post_type=awards&#038;p=203', 0, 'awards', '', 0),
(204, 1, '2014-01-21 20:43:18', '2014-01-21 20:43:18', 'Oakwood was awarded Asia''s Leading Serviced Apartment Brand at the World Travel Awards (WTA) for the Asia, Australasia & Indian Ocean regions – the first year for this category. The WTA awards programme, hailed as the ''Oscars of the travel industry'' by the global media, highlights and rewards those travel brands that have made the greatest contribution to the industry over the past year.', 'World Travel Awards', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'world-travel-awards', '', '', '2014-01-21 20:43:18', '2014-01-21 20:43:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/2014/?post_type=awards&#038;p=204', 0, 'awards', '', 0),
(205, 1, '2014-01-21 20:45:38', '2014-01-21 20:45:38', 'In 2008, Oakwood won the coveted Tower of Excellence Award in the Most Creative Marketing, Large Provider category for the second consecutive year. The CHPA''s Most Creative Marketing Award recognizes an outstanding marketing program or concept that had a measurable impact on the organization.', 'Corporate Housing Providers Association', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'corporate-housing-providers-association', '', '', '2014-01-21 20:45:38', '2014-01-21 20:45:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/2014/?post_type=awards&#038;p=205', 0, 'awards', '', 0),
